TY  - JOUR
T1  - Stability and Preference Alignment in Matching and Coalition Formation
AU  - Pycia, Marek
Y1  - 2012/01/01
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2012/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA7143
T2  - Econometrica
